('Gallium aluminium arsenide (GaAlAs) laser', 'Reduction in colony count of P. intermedia after being exposed to GaAlAs diode laser for 1 minute from 369-229, 134 and 41; decrease in colony count of P. gingivalis after being exposed to GaAlAs diode laser for 1 minute from 286.52-197, 94 and 39,', '', 'Photodynamic therapy (PDT) kills the bacteria and also leads to the detoxification of endotoxins.', 31235678),
